  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merchant 64 is a low-poly 3D adventure game and a short, heartfelt love letter to late-90s gaming.<strong></strong><br><br><strong>A  TEENY TINY ADVENTURE   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small game designed to be a delightful, short adventure with multiple endings.    <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>MAKE THE BIG BUCKS<br> </strong>In this adventure, take control of Merchant as you buy goods at low prices and sell them for profit in different towns.<strong>  </strong><br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>TRAVERSE ACROSS TOWNS<br> </strong>As a traveling merchant, you’ll need to explore the world and journey to new towns to sell your goods.<strong>  </strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>PURCHASE UPGRADES   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your adventure, purchase various upgrades to aid you on your merchant journey!    <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merchant 64 is a low-poly 3D adventure game and a short, heartfelt love letter to late-90s gaming.<strong></strong><br><br><strong>A  TEENY TINY ADVENTURE   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a small game designed to be a delightful, short adventure with multiple endings.    <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/9f3e7aa04db52953e6e7007e4cd573ed.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>MAKE THE BIG BUCKS<br> </strong>In this adventure, take control of Merchant as you buy goods at low prices and sell them for profit in different towns.<strong>  </strong><br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/c6e41e63a04a545def7a89b58a9baae4.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>TRAVERSE ACROSS TOWNS<br> </strong>As a traveling merchant, you’ll need to explore the world and journey to new towns to sell your goods.<strong>  </strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/94ee4dde26c335d1834c8794339c2e30.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>PURCHASE UPGRADES   </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your adventure, purchase various upgrades to aid you on your merchant journey!    <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.poster.avif?t=1743404432\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.webm?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440000/extras/60844bd69fa157922ec1335f23649c08.mp4?t=1743404432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
